      "height": 240,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "groupIds": [],
      "text": "Legend:\n• Green: Presentation Layer (Controllers)\n• Blue: Service Layer (Business Logic)\n• Orange: Data Access Layer (Repositories)\n• Gray: External Systems\n\nTechnology Stack:\n• Java 17 + Spring Boot 2.7\n• Spring Security + JWT\n• Spring Data JPA\n• PostgreSQL Database\n• Docker Containerization",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "index": "aL",
