      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Legend:\n• Green: Presentation Layer (Controllers)\n• Blue: Service Layer (Business Logic)\n• Orange: Data Access Layer (Repositories)\n• Gray: External Systems\n\nTechnology Stack:\n• Java 17 + Spring Boot 2.7\n• Spring Security + JWT\n• Spring Data JPA\n• PostgreSQL Database\n• Docker Containerization",
